function_call.arguments: {"risks":[{"Description":"Focus on general mosquito bite prevention may overshadow the importance of disease prevention messages.","Impact":"Increased risk of disease transmission and outbreaks.","Mitigation":"Balanced messaging on both general mosquito bite prevention and vector-borne disease transmission prevention.","Technologies":"Public health communication strategies and campaigns.","People":"General public, especially those living in areas with high mosquito activity.","Owner":"Public health organizations and government health authorities."}]}
